OL,3,COvo boss says Labour should launch
OL,4,Csocial tariff to tackle rising energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FThe boss of Ovo Energy has called for
OL,8,Fsweeping changes to the UK's energy
OL,9,Fbills system so they are subsidised
OL,10,Ffor poorer households, as consumers
OL,11,Fface another rise in fuel costs this
OL,12,Fwinter.
OL,14,FChief executive David Buttress told
OL,15,Fthe PA news agency the Government
OL,16,Fshould introduce a social tariff,
OL,17,Fsomething which is already used in the
OL,18,Ftelecoms industry to help people who
OL,19,Freceive benefits like Universal Credit
OL,20,Fpay their broadband bills.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
