OL,3,COvo boss says Labour should launch
OL,4,Csocial tariff to tackle rising energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FIt comes as the average household
OL,8,Fenergy bill is set to rise by #149
OL,9,Ffrom October 1 after industry watchdog
OL,10,FOfgem increased its price cap.
OL,12,FOvo, which is the fourth-biggest
OL,13,Fdomestic electricity provider in the
OL,14,FUK, recently announced a fresh #50
OL,15,Fmillion energy bills support scheme
OL,16,Ffor the winter months.
OL,18,FBut Mr Buttress said Labour should aim
OL,19,Fto "get away from the short-term
OL,20,Ftactics" of tackling high energy bills
OL,21,Fvia handouts on a year-by-year basis.
