OL,3,COvo boss says Labour should launch
OL,4,Csocial tariff to tackle rising energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FMinisters asked firms about longer
OL,8,Fterm market reforms for energy bills
OL,9,Fincluding a social tariff at a
OL,10,Froundtable at the end of August, which
OL,11,FOvo attended.
OL,13,FMr Buttress told PA the Government
OL,14,Fshould "be pragmatic ... and look at
OL,15,Fthe most efficient way" to fund it,
OL,16,Fwhether that be through increases to
OL,17,Feveryone else's energy bills or via
OL,18,Fgeneral taxation.
