OL,3,COvo boss says Labour should launch
OL,4,Csocial tariff to tackle rising energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FThe latest increase in energy bills
OL,8,Fcomes as the Government continues to
OL,9,Fface criticism over its plans to
OL,10,Frestrict winter fuel payments to those
OL,11,Freceiving Pension Credit.
OL,13,FIt means around 10 million people will
OL,14,Flose out this winter, with the benefit
OL,15,Ftaken away from all but the poorest
OL,16,Fpensioners in the country. About 11.5
OL,17,Fmillion people used to receive it.
