OL,3,COvo boss says Labour should launch
OL,4,Csocial tariff to tackle rising energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FSpeaking about the policy, Mr Buttress
OL,8,Fsaid: "You have to look at it in the
OL,9,Fround. The Government has come in and
OL,10,Fhad to take a view of the various
OL,11,Fdifferent mechanisms and schemes, as
OL,12,Fwell as the new Budget at the end of
OL,13,FOctober."
OL,15,FHe added: "We must have a grown-up
OL,16,Fconversation about how we protect the
OL,17,Fmost vulnerable... A social tariff
OL,18,Fwill protect all those that need that
OL,19,Fextra help with the cost of energy,
OL,20,Fnot just one group or another."
